l-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Теперь откройте файл конфигурации WordPress:</span></p><ul style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;\"><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Courier New\';color:#323232;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.295;background-color:#ffffff;margin-top:14pt;margin-bottom:14pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Courier New\';color:#323232;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">sudo nano /var/www/</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Courier New\';color:#e94849;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">wordpress</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Courier New\';color:#323232;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">/wp-config.php</span><span style=\"font-size:6.999999999999999pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';color:#323232;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Courier New\';color:#323232;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-al